{"tid":1651861,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得真係開始有本錢搞港獨?","createTime":"2019-10-13T13:11:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T14:46:54.000Z","uid":273621,"like":11,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"977ecb265b7f58e44995ebbbdaaa6cb7925ebae5","tid":1651861,"uid":273621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:11:47.000Z","msg":"港獨搞唔起當然係因為無軍力,無資源,<br />\n而且最重要既係獨立成國要其他國家認同先有可能。<br />\n<br />\n但經過最近幾個月,香港人既族群意識開始成形,<br />\n出現一種唔係基於中國人身份認同既香港人身份,<br />\n細良話呢場運動會漸漸比中共逼成獨立運動。<br />\n的確由「香港人加油」到「願榮光歸香港」,都係反映「香港人」既身份愈黎愈獨立於中國人身份既基礎。<br />\n<br />\n而且依家開始全世界都係度叫&quot;Free Hong Kong&quot;<br />\n&quot;Free Hong Kong&quot;諗真d其實唔係爭取民主既口號,係爭取獨立、爭取解放既口號喎。<br />\n<br />\n「光復香港 時代革命」係香港通常係翻譯成 &quot;Free Hong Kong, <strong>Revolution of our Time</strong>&quot;<br />\n但外國好多文宣都係直接寫&quot;Free Hong Kong, Revolution <strong>Now</strong>&quot;<br />\n後者除左短d順口d,仲係完全不避諱獨立既可能性。<br />\n<br />\n香港想獨立,隨係會有外國支持,<br />\n尤其係大陸接管香港呢個安排本身就有問題。(例如南京條約唔係同中共簽,係同滿清簽。)<br />\n係呢個全球各國圍攻中國既形勢底下,自然有更多國家會為左打擊中國而支持香港獨立。<br />\n<br />\n我地係咪要開始直接同習大大講價?<br />\n下次林鄭再有對話會,或者民間記者會,係咪可以試下搵人講<br />\n<br />\n一係就<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>真雙普選</strong></span>,一係就<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香港獨立</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n利申:<br />\n其實只要保障到人權自由法治呢d核心價值,獨唔獨我本人係無乜所謂。但獨立好似真係愈黎愈有可能。"},{"pid":"ee4624927150ff083bd5ab805ff56a2e1dc077b9","tid":1651861,"uid":37771,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:13:07.000Z","msg":"獨立唔係重點, 重點係五大, 拉"},{"pid":"3f0f7c57756b21d735bb66e740767f854b9654be","tid":1651861,"uid":5523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:13:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V7chn1QDDGQ&amp;t=85s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DV7chn1QDDGQ%26t%3D85s&d=uxh%2FksCcDU8UuFRsnlXnuVUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=2bb62ab1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V7chn1QDDGQ&amp;t=85s</a><br />\n<br />\n可以搞<br />\n但唔係依家<br />\n我都想搞<br />\n但睇美帝頭<br />\n等佢幫我地搞左5 demands先"},{"pid":"34b51aad05a53479bcd309215dd8404f73c07b77","tid":1651861,"uid":273621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:13:31.000Z","msg":"嘩邊個秒速負評咁勁"},{"pid":"5c7b9ce6052b47e4fc35d71c5c355a7c609ac4c6","tid":1651861,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:14:08.000Z","msg":"有野想捐可以FB搵我地香港自由之書阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[澄清]國難五金課金問題&mdash;照舊課！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nFB: 國難五金, 香港自由之書<br />\n<br />\n虛心求教<br />\n你望下連登都成日比人帶風向 你真係有信心搞得成獨立之後RUN到?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBTW 之前唔係組左臨時議會咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7718ef836697ed6f0aa360681ef8c1094eb9504d","tid":1651861,"uid":277144,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:14:16.000Z","msg":"雙普選未等如獨立囉，傻豬"},{"pid":"a280b88fa96ab2e90721ced09ccd0bf457aa9b7d","tid":1651861,"uid":99466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:14:58.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"8fcb535ebc7798437bf17a7f1fd7ba0cdaa18917","tid":1651861,"uid":273621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7718ef836697ed6f0aa360681ef8c1094eb9504d","tid":1651861,"uid":277144,"like":1,"dislike